    • countPointInPolygon

      public static org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection countPointInPolygon​(org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection pointsCollec, java.lang.String namePoint, org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection polygonsCollec, boolean keepAttributes)
      Count points that are included in every polygons of a collection. Doesn't keep the polygon attributes.
      Parameters:
      pointsCollec - Point collection
      namePoint - Name of the points that are added (goes in the count attribute name)
      polygonsCollec - Polygon collection
      keepAttributes - If true, keep every attributes of the input polygon collection
      Returns:
      the Polygon collection with a new field count.

    • countPointInPolygon

      public static org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection countPointInPolygon​(org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection pointsCollec, java.lang.String namePoint, org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection polygonsCollec, boolean keepAttributes, java.util.List<java.lang.String> attrsToDescriptiveStat, java.util.List<java.lang.String> attrsToCensusStat, java.util.List<StatisticOperation> statsToDo)
      Count points that are included in every polygons of a collection
      Parameters:
      pointsCollec - Point collection
      namePoint - Name of the points that are added (goes in the count attribute name)
      polygonsCollec - Polygon collection
      keepAttributes - If true, keep every attributes of the input polygon collection
      attrsToDescriptiveStat - List of attributes for which descriptive statistics will be calculated
      attrsToCensusStat - List of attributes for which every occurrence will be counted
      statsToDo - Which descriptive statistics are calculated
      Returns:
      the Polygon collection with a new field count and new fields depending on the attributes calculations
